a2t.text_actual: Refill prescriptions faster, get photo prints in about an hour, and know the deals before you shop. PHARMACY FEATURES • Refill by Scan* - Refill prescriptions by simply scanning your Rx label. Get 500 Balance® Rewards points for every refill.**  • Pill Reminder – Get reminded to take your prescriptions and over-the-counter medications and vitamins • Transfer Prescription – Easily transfer your prescriptions to Walgreens • Refill Reminders – Receive alerts when it’s time to refill your prescriptions • Pharmacy Chat – Get health advice and account support from a pharmacy professional • Healthcare Clinic – Find a location and schedule appointments  • Rx Info & Updates – Access your Rx history and status PHOTO FEATURES  • QuickPrints – Print photos from your phone, Facebook, Instagram and Walgreens.com albums. Pick up at your local Walgreens in about an hour  • Photo Cards – Create flat and folded photo cards with photos from your phone and pick up the same day (Available on Android 4.0 and above) • Photo Editing – Edit your photos using filters and a variety of editing tools • Poster and Canvas Prints – Turn your favorite photos into posters and Canvas Prints. (Available on Android 4.0 and above) • Collage Prints– Design unique collage prints with photos from your phone, Facebook and Instagram albums BALANCE® REWARDS FEATURES • Scan your mobile card at checkout to earn points, check your point status and apply savings from your clipped coupons  • Check your point status wherever you are • View and manage your clipped coupons   SHOPPING FEATURES • Weekly Ad & Coupons - Find exclusive deals and savings every week. Clip manufacturers’ coupons and coupons from the Weekly Ad to your Balance® Rewards. Redeem in store by scanning your mobile card at checkout  • In-Store Experience – Easily access the tools you need when you shop in store   • Promos & Offers –Find exclusive deals and limited-time offers • Coupons Widget – Preview coupons from your home screen • Store Maps – Use your Shopping List to locate products in the store   • Local Shopping – Set your preferred store and search store inventory  • Scanner - Learn about products by scanning barcodes in the Weekly Ad  NOTES ON PERMISSIONS Permissions help you access specific app functions and features • Contact permissions share your Shopping List with your contacts via Weekly Ad & Coupons feature • Calendar permissions add Healthcare Clinic appointments to your calendar • Location permissions display nearby stores and map out directions • Screen permissions adjust the display when you rotate your device • Telephony permissions let you call a Walgreens store from the app • Camera, Vibrate Flashlight and Wi-Fi permissions use the Transfer Prescription by Scan and Refill by Scan features • Store and Receive Boot Completed permissions store non-personal information—such as reminders There is no charge to download the Walgreens App, but specified rates from your wireless provider and other fees as noted in your Walgreens account agreement(s) still apply. ** Due to state and federal laws, points cannot be earned on some items. Points will not be awarded to anyone who currently is or was at any time in the 6 months prior to purchasing Pharmacy Items covered by Medicare, Medicaid, Tricare or any other government-funded healthcare program. Pharmacy Items must be purchased at participating Walgreens Drugstore, Rxpress, Duane Reade, or Walgreens Pharmacy locations ("Participating Stores") to earn points. Excludes Pharmacy Items purchased from AR, NJ or NY pharmacies and prescriptions transferred to a Participating Store located in AL, MS, OR or PR. See Balance Rewards terms and conditions for full details
